title: Deadmau5 vs Daft Punk Mega-Mix Re-Make
description: [Download Link: https://www.facebook.com/pages/Booda-...] Took about like a month or two to get this done. By far the only thing that was hard to do on this mix was trying to keep up the pace in the beginning and trying to transition between the songs in the beginning. Hopefully, I think it's good or probably my best well dedicated mix i made in a while. Also, it took me two weeks to edit all of this because I wanted to be like the last mix. Hope you people like it and kind of give you an idea of how I want the Deadmau5 vs Daft Punk Mega-Mix 2 to be like :D. ----------------------------------------­----------------------------------------­-----------------Links: Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pages/Booda-...
